## Correction 3: keep tactical v1 minimal but leave model windows intact

Your instinct that the tactical oracle should only care about win-in-1 / lose-in-1 is good for v1.

But the **model** should still see `WINDOW6` tokens. That is not the same as a complex tactical oracle. The reports strongly recommend window objects because Hexo tactics are naturally represented through six-cell windows and legal-cell/window relations. 

So the update should be:

```text
